</p>
<p>of peaceful assembly and of association, 22/6 of 21 March 2013, on protecting human 
</p>
<p>rights defenders, 22/10 of 21 March 2013 on the promotion and protection of human rights 
</p>
<p>in the context of peaceful protests, 21/32 of 28 September 2012, on the right to 
</p>
<p>development, 22/31 of 22 March 2013, on combating intolerance, negative stereotyping and 
</p>
<p>stigmatization of, and discrimination, incitement to violence and violence against, persons 
</p>
<p>based on religion or belief, and 23/3 of 13 June 2013 on the enhancement of international 
</p>
<p>cooperation in the field of human rights, 
